translations: n．犬科动物分娩：指犬科动物（如狗、狼等）的雌性动物生产幼崽的过程。
· The dog is whelping in the corner.
那只狗在角落里生产幼崽。
v．生产幼崽：指犬科动物的雌性动物生产幼崽。

phrs.translation: 玄色小龙, 黑色小龙, 黑色虬龙

sentences.sentence: It is a good idea to build a whelping box well in advance so the bitch has time to get used to it.
sentences.translation: 最好预先为母犬建一个产箱，这样母犬可以有时间去适应。

sentences.sentence: The next area to question is the whelping of the puppies.
sentences.translation: 问题的另一方面就是幼崽的。

sentences.sentence: The chicken flapping claws onto the roost its wings whelping and walloping.
sentences.translation: 小鸡挥动着爪子跳到栖木上，稚嫩的翅膀不停拍打着。
